headline: Allied Global Marketing Names Reina Basu Vice President of Business Development, Accelerating Global Brand Experience Strategy
summary: Allied Global Marketing (AGM) has appointed Reina Basu as Vice President of Business Development, supporting the continued global expansion of its Brand Experience division.
